Cuidado con los mensajes del día de los enamorados
Sobre todo, a quién se los mandas: <a href="http://www.abc.net.au/news/newsitems/200602/s1567808.htm">Warning for Valentine's texters</a>.

<blockquote>
Recipients of the unwanted texts include bosses or colleagues (9 per cent),
parents (3 per cent) and perhaps most embarrassing of all, ex-partners (2
per cent).
</blockquote>

Visto en <a href="http://www.smartmobs.com/archive/2006/02/11/valentines_day.html">Valentine's day and SMS</a>.


